538
00:37:41,533 --> 00:37:42,966
That is less than one-tenth of the total.

539
00:37:45,466 --> 00:37:46,200
What is your view?

540
00:37:47,700 --> 00:37:50,300
Father befriended the current Emperor in humble times.

541
